Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.49,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}若如你所言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.49,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}だとすれば
